Name: Ambient Pressure
Description: Barometric ambient pressure from baro sensor

Name: MAP (Manifold Absolute Pressure)
Description: Absolute manifold pressure (subtract baro for boost)

Name: Torque Request (Driver)
Description: Requested engine torque from driver input

Name: Spark Advance Base Map
Description: Base spark advance value from calibration maps

Name: STFT Bank 1
Description: Alternate short term fuel trim representation

Name: LTFT Bank 1
Description: Alternate long term fuel trim representation

Name: Cylinder Injection Timing 1
Description: Commanded injector pulse width for cylinder 1

Name: Cylinder Injection Timing 2
Description: Commanded injector pulse width for cylinder 2

Name: Cylinder Injection Timing 3
Description: Commanded injector pulse width for cylinder 3

Name: Torque Model Output Index
Description: Index used to look up torque model outputs

Name: Adaptive Boost Trim
Description: Boost trim applied by adaptation algorithms

Name: Final Torque Limit (Dynamic)
Description: Post-intervention torque limit applied by ECU

Name: Gear-Based Torque Cap
Description: Torque cap values indexed by gear

Name: Turbo Overboost Allowed
Description: Absolute MAP ceiling permitted by ECU

Name: Wastegate Duty Raw
Description: Raw wastegate PWM before driver stage

Name: Boost PID Integrator State
Description: Integrator memory for boost PID controller

Name: Component Limiting Source
Description: Which subsystem is enforcing a limit

Name: ECU Thermal Margin
Description: Thermal margin estimate for derate decisions

Name: Torque Intervention Reason
Description: Bitmask describing why torque was limited

Name: Launch Control Active
Description: Launch control enable flag (usually disabled in production)

Name: Last Security Event
Description: Timestamp of most recent security access attempt

Name: Last Torque Intervention Timestamp
Description: Time of last torque intervention event
